Forewords: This Device Adapter covers laser combiners only. For stand-alone LaserBoxx sources, refer to the device adapter named [[Oxxius]].

==Combiner Hub==
This Hub provides access to the laser sources, the accessories and various components connected to (or mounted in) an Oxxius combiner. The hub's "chidren" are detailed in the following paragraphs.

Hub properties:
    Serial number (read only)
    Interlock status (read only)
    Emission key status (read only)

==LaserBoxx source==
Inheritance: CShutterBase.
Available properties:
    Status (read only)
    Alarm (read only)
    Control mode: ACC or APC (read and write)
    Modulation selection: analog and digital (read and write)
    Current set point, as a percentage of the nominal current (read and write)
    Power set point, as a percentage of the nominal power (read and write)
    Emission status: "off" or "on" (read and write)

==Known limitations==
* Requires firmware version 1.0.17 or higher. Use the query "?SV" to get your version number.
* Cobolt laser sources not yet supported.

